data.text:
Albion Canvas

Following the announcement of Boldscan going into receivership, Clear Sky are very pleased to announce that they have now finalised the on boarding of the Albion Canvas brand and customer base.

Clear sky sees this as a strategic move for our company that ensures the Albion customers will be able to access the experienced support and industry knowledge that Clear Sky is renowned for.

We are currently working on a new web site and branding and our plans for a new range of innovative canvas designs

During the coming few weeks we will make contact with all the existing clients of Albion to ascertain where we can help with the current tents as well as discussing any future tents that they may be planning.

For all the Albion customers, Clear Sky will be pleased to arrange an initial site visit free of charge to discuss any issues or concerns they may have and to discuss any future development or expansion plans.

In the first instance, call Mark on 0333 241 2660 or email mark.scott@safaritents.net #albioncanvas http://albioncanvas.net/
